name: Frank Inu
description: Frank Inu collection will become the biggest symbol of status in the universe. Frank Inu’s vision is to bring fun into the crypt movements, create value and rewards for our holders. Frankn Inu wants to bring a whole new innovation to our holders and crypto space. Not only a crypto coin but a whole new way of crypto! Our unique NFT collection and merchandise will be a cool “wow factor” for not only investors but your everyday person. We will be adding in staking as well as staking benefits towards weNFTs. Who ever stakes a certain amount will receive future weNFTS benefits and access to future fashion show. We want to build the best community there is and see the cool NFTS people mint while also getting those who stick around giveaways, fire sales, etc. We want this community to be a family and we hope that a lot of people see Frank Inu as theirs too.
